    path: /workspace/PF5_TO_PF6_MIGRATION_CHECKLIST.md
    content: # PatternFly 5 → PatternFly 6 Migration Checklist

> **Source**: Official PatternFly upgrade guide (https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/),
> pf-codemods README (https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods), and PatternFly 6 release notes.
> Current PF6 version: **6.4.0**

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Package & Dependency Changes](#1-package--dependency-changes)
2. [CSS Token & Variable System Overhaul](#2-css-token--variable-system-overhaul)
3. [CSS Class Name Changes](#3-css-class-name-changes)
4. [Component Breaking Changes (by component)](#4-component-breaking-changes)
5. [Removed / Deprecated Components](#5-removed--deprecated-components)
6. [Charts Library Changes](#6-charts-library-changes)
7. [Icon Changes](#7-icon-changes)
8. [Toolbar Overhaul](#8-toolbar-overhaul)
9. [Page & Layout Changes](#9-page--layout-changes)
10. [Breakpoint Changes](#10-breakpoint-changes)
11. [Test Impact & Potential Failures](#11-test-impact--potential-failures)
12. [Codemods Tool Reference](#12-codemods-tool-reference)
13. [Migration Workflow (step-by-step)](#13-migration-workflow)

---

## 1. Package & Dependency Changes

### Package Name Updates
| PF5 Package | PF6 Package | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `@patternfly/react-core` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-core` (v6) | Same name, major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-table` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-table` (v6) | Same name, major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-charts` (v6) | Import paths changed (see Charts section) |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-icons` (v6) | Same name, major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-tokens` (v6) | Token naming completely changed |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-styles` (v6) | CSS module references updated |
| `@patternfly/react-component-groups` (v5) | `@patternfly/react-component-groups` (v6) | Many renames (see below) |

### Import Path Changes
- [ ] **Deprecated components** now import from `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`
- [ ] **Next/promoted components** (Modal, DualListSelector) now import from `@patternfly/react-core` (not `/next`)
- [ ] **Charts**: `@patternfly/react-charts` → `@patternfly/react-charts/victory`
- [ ] **Victory** is now an optional peer dependency — install `victory` or specific packages (`victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, etc.)

### Checklist
- [ ] Update all `@patternfly/*` packages to v6
- [ ] Install Victory as a peer dependency if using charts
- [ ] Run `npm install` / `yarn install` to resolve peer dependency warnings
- [ ] Verify no PF5 packages remain in `package.json`

---

## 2. CSS Token & Variable System Overhaul

### What Changed
PatternFly 6 introduces a **design token system** that completely replaces the old CSS variable naming:
- **Old**: `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` or `--pf-v5-c-button--...`
- **New**: `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` (semantic tokens with `--pf-t--` prefix)

### Key Naming Pattern Changes
| PF5 Pattern | PF6 Pattern |
|---|---|
| `--pf-v5-global--*` | `--pf-t--global--*` (design tokens) |
| `--pf-v5-c-{component}--*` | `--pf-v6-c-{component}--*` (component vars) |
| `pf-v5-c-*` (CSS classes) | `pf-v6-c-*` (CSS classes) |
| `pf-v5-l-*` (layout classes) | `pf-v6-l-*` (layout classes) |
| `pf-v5-u-*` (utility classes) | `pf-v6-u-*` (utility classes) |

### React Token Changes
| PF5 React Token | PF6 React Token |
|---|---|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| `global_link_Color_hover` | `t_global_color_nonstatus_*_clicked` (varies) |
| `color_green_10` | `t_color_green_10` |

### Color Prop Renames
| Old Color | New Color |
|---|---|
| `cyan` | `teal` |
| `gold` | `yellow` |

### Checklist
- [ ] Run `tokens-update` codemod for React tokens in `.js`/`.tsx` files
- [ ] Run `css-vars-updater` codemod for CSS variables in `.css`/`.scss`/`.md` files
- [ ] Run `class-name-updater --v6 --fix` codemod for CSS class names
- [ ] Manually replace `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` hot pink placeholders with correct tokens
- [ ] Manually replace `t_temp_dev_tbd` React token placeholders
- [ ] Remove all CSS overrides targeting old PF5 variables (they no longer work)
- [ ] Review [removed variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [ ] Review [added variables spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)
- [ ] Replace `color='cyan'` → `color='teal'` on Banner and Label
- [ ] Replace `color='gold'` → `color='yellow'` on Banner and Label

---

## 3. CSS Class Name Changes

### Global Pattern
All CSS classes change from `pf-v5-*` to `pf-v6-*`:
- `pf-v5-c-button` → `pf-v6-c-button`
- `pf-v5-l-flex` → `pf-v6-l-flex`
- `pf-v5-u-mt-md` → `pf-v6-u-mt-md`

### Logical Direction Changes
CSS variables using physical direction (Left/Right) are replaced with logical direction (InsetInlineStart/InsetInlineEnd):
- `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--Left` → `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--InsetInlineStart`

### Checklist
- [ ] Run `class-name-updater --v6 --fix` across the codebase
- [ ] Search for hardcoded `pf-v5-` in all files and replace with `pf-v6-`
- [ ] Update any test selectors that reference PF class names
- [ ] Update any snapshot tests

---

## 4. Component Breaking Changes

### Button
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|---|---|---|
| `isActive` → `isClicked` | Prop renamed | ✅ Auto-fix |
| Icons must use `icon` prop | Icons no longer go as children; pass to `icon` prop instead. For `variant="plain"`, children are moved to `icon` automatically. | ✅ Auto-fix (partial) |
| `isDisabled` → uses `disabled` attr | No longer sets `aria-disabled` on native buttons; `aria-disabled` only renders when `true` | ⚠️ Manual test updates |
| Text wrapper `<span>` added | Button text is now wrapped in `<span class="pf-v6-c-button__text">` | ⚠️ Test selectors may break |
| `button-support-favorite-variant` | `variant="plain"` with `isFavorite` updated | ✅ Auto-fix |

### EmptyState ⚠️ MAJOR REFACTOR
| Change | Details | Codemod |
|---|---|---|
| `EmptyStateHeader` removed | No longer a separate component; use `titleText`, `headingLevel`, `icon` props on `<EmptyState>` directly | ✅ Partial auto-fix |
| `EmptyStateIcon` removed | Pass icon component directly to `icon` prop on `<EmptyState>` (e.g., `icon={CubesIcon}`) | ✅ Partial auto-fix |
| `EmptyStateHeader`/`EmptyStateIcon` no longer exported | Remove imports | ✅ Auto-fix |
| `headerClassName` prop added | Replaces `className` that was on `EmptyStateHeader` | ✅ Auto-fix |
| **May require manual updates** | Complex EmptyState layouts need manual review | ⚠️ Manual |

**PF5 → PF6 EmptyState pattern:**
```tsx
// PF5
<EmptyState>
  <EmptyStateHeader titleText="Title" headingLevel="h4"
    icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={CubesIcon} />} />
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>

// PF6
<EmptyState titleText="Title" headingLevel="h4" icon={CubesIcon}>
  <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
</EmptyState>
```

