## 6. Charts Library Changes

### Import Path Change
```tsx
// PF5
import { Chart, ChartArea } from '@patternfly/react-charts';

// PF6
import { Chart, ChartArea } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';
```

### Victory Peer Dependency
Victory is now an **optional peer dependency**. Install one of:
- `victory` (all features)
- Individual packages: `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, `victory-chart`, etc.

### Checklist
- [ ] Update all `@patternfly/react-charts` imports to `@patternfly/react-charts/victory`
- [ ] Install Victory as a peer dependency
- [ ] Verify chart rendering after migration

---

## 7. Icon Changes

### Button Icon Prop
Icons in buttons must now use the `icon` prop:
```tsx
// PF5
<Button variant="plain"><TimesIcon /></Button>

// PF6
<Button variant="plain" icon={<TimesIcon />} />
```

### NavItem Icon Prop
NavItem has a new `icon` prop for icons (instead of embedding in children).

### Checklist
- [ ] Move all button icons from children to `icon` prop
- [ ] Move NavItem icons to `icon` prop
- [ ] Update icon-only MenuToggle instances

